Warehouse

Database
	PostgresSQL Database will be used
		*Development database ==> warehouse_development
		*Testing database ==> warehouse_testing
		*Production database ==> warehouse_production

Authentication
	3 Type of Users
		*Internal User
		*External User
		*Administration
	
	Registration can only be done by ADMINISTRATOR
	User registration and Log In will be managed with Devise
	Roles will be defined with rolify
	Authorization will be managed with CanCanCan (Continuation of CanCan)
	
	Basic Atributes ==>	Name
						Last Name
						Email
						Password
	
